00:09:05.700 --> 00:09:06.890
Gin-san!  

00:09:09.630 --> 00:09:12.950
G-Gin-san...  

00:09:13.390 --> 00:09:14.970
Shinpachi!  

00:09:14.970 --> 00:09:18.100
